### Request email code (dev shows code in response)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/request-email-code
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "username": "{{username}}"
}

### Verify email with code
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "code": "{{code}}",
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "characterName": "Hero_{{username}}",
  "className": "warrior"
}


